#: ../../source/scene.rst:4
msgid "Scene Setup"
msgstr "场景设置"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:6
msgid ""
"This panel provides access to configure *Timeline*, *Rigid Body World*, "
"and *Bake*."
msgstr "该面板提供了配置 *时间轴（Timeline）*、*刚体世界（Rigid Body World）* 以及 *烘焙（Bake）* 的入口。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:8
msgid "Scene Setup panel"
msgstr "场景设置面板"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:16
msgid "Timeline"
msgstr "时间轴"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:18
msgid "The *Timeline* section displays and edits basic animation frame settings:"
msgstr "*时间轴* 部分用于显示和编辑基本的动画帧设置："

#: ../../source/scene.rst:20
msgid "``Current Frame``: Displays the current frame of the scene timeline."
msgstr "``Current Frame``：显示场景时间轴的当前帧。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:21
msgid ""
"``Start`` / ``End``: Defines the playback range used for previewing and "
"baking physics simulations."
msgstr "``Start`` / ``End``：定义预览和烘焙物理模拟的播放范围。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:23
msgid "These values are shared with Blender's main timeline."
msgstr "这些值与 Blender 的主时间轴同步。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:26
msgid "Rigid Body World"
msgstr "刚体世界"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:28
msgid ""
"Blender's rigid body system relies on a scene-level container called the "
"*Rigid Body World*, which manages:"
msgstr "Blender 的刚体系统依赖于一个场景级容器 *刚体世界（Rigid Body World）*，它管理："

#: ../../source/scene.rst:30
msgid "Global simulation settings (*solver iterations*, *substeps*, *gravity*)"
msgstr "全局模拟设置（*求解迭代次数（solver iterations）*、*子步数（substeps）*、*重力（gravity）*）"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:31
msgid "Collections that store rigid bodies"
msgstr "存放刚体（*Rigid Body*）的集合"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:32
msgid "Collections that store rigid body constraints"
msgstr "存放刚体约束（*Rigid Body Constraints*）的集合"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:34
msgid "This add-on automatically manages these settings to ensure consistency."
msgstr "本插件会自动管理这些设置，以保证一致性。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:39
msgid "Update Rigid World"
msgstr "更新刚体世界"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:41
msgid ""
"Blender requires all rigid bodies and constraints to be placed in "
"specific collections referenced by the *Rigid Body World*."
msgstr "Blender 要求所有刚体和约束都必须放置在 *刚体世界（Rigid Body World）* 所指定的集合中。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:43
msgid ""
"Click :menuselection:`Update Rigid World` to synchronize the scene with "
"the rigid body system and ensure that all add-on objects are correctly "
"registered in the required collections."
msgstr ""
"点击 :menuselection:`Update Rigid World` "
"以将场景与刚体系统同步，确保所有插件对象都正确注册到刚体世界所使用的集合中。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:51
msgid "This operation will:"
msgstr "该操作将会："

#: ../../source/scene.rst:53
msgid "Ensure a valid *Rigid Body World* exists in the scene"
msgstr "确保场景中存在有效的 *刚体世界（Rigid Body World）*"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:54
msgid "Create and assign required collections if missing"
msgstr "缺少集合时，创建并分配必要的集合"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:55
msgid "Add all rigid bodies to the world collection"
msgstr "将所有 *刚体（Rigid Body）* 添加到世界集合中"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:56
msgid "Add all rigid body constraints to the constraint collection"
msgstr "将所有 *刚体约束（Rigid Body Constraint）* 添加到约束集合中"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:57
msgid "Fix broken references caused by:"
msgstr "修复因以下原因导致的断链引用："

#: ../../source/scene.rst:59
msgid "Linked files"
msgstr "链接文件"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:60
msgid "Library Overrides"
msgstr "库覆盖"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:61
msgid "Collection instances"
msgstr "实例化集合"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:64
msgid ""
"If the button shows a warning icon, it indicates that the *Rigid Body "
"World* settings differ from the recommended defaults and should be "
"updated."
msgstr "如果按钮显示警告图标，说明 *刚体世界（Rigid Body World）* 的设置与推荐默认值不同，需要更新。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:66
msgid ""
"This operator is safe to run at any time and is recommended whenever the "
"scene structure changes."
msgstr "该操作可随时安全运行，建议在场景结构发生变化时使用。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:69
msgid "Why :menuselection:`Update Rigid World` Is Needed"
msgstr "为什么需要 :menuselection:`Update Rigid World`"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:71
msgid "Blender's rigid body system relies on two internal collections:"
msgstr "Blender 的刚体系统依赖于两个内部集合："

#: ../../source/scene.rst:73
msgid "A collection containing all rigid body objects"
msgstr "存放所有刚体的集合"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:74
msgid "A collection containing all rigid body constraints"
msgstr "存放所有刚体约束的集合"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:76
msgid ""
"When rigs are linked, duplicated, or overridden, these references may "
"become outdated or invalid."
msgstr "当骨架被链接、复制或覆写时，这些引用可能会变得过时或无效。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:78
msgid ""
"The :menuselection:`Update Rigid World` operation rebuilds these "
"references and ensures that all add-on objects are correctly registered "
"in the simulation system."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Update Rigid World` 操作会重建这些引用，并确保所有插件对象正确注册到模拟系统中。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:81
msgid "Simulation Quality Settings"
msgstr "模拟质量设置"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:83
msgid "The following parameters control simulation accuracy and stability:"
msgstr "以下参数用于控制模拟的精度与稳定性："

#: ../../source/scene.rst:85
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Substeps`: Number of physics substeps per frame. Higher "
"values improve stability for fast-moving or lightweight objects."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Substeps`：每帧的物理子步数。值越高，快速移动或轻量物体的稳定性越好。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:86
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Iterations`: Solver iteration count per substep. Higher "
"values result in more accurate constraint solving at the cost of "
"performance."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Iterations`：每个子步的求解迭代次数。值越高，约束求解越精确，但会牺牲性能。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:89
msgid "These parameters correspond to Blender's Bullet physics solver settings."
msgstr "这些参数对应 Blender 的 Bullet 物理求解器设置。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:91
msgid ""
"The add-on provides default values for these parameters based on "
"practical experience, balancing stability and performance."
msgstr "插件根据经验为这些参数设置了默认值，以在稳定性和性能之间取得平衡。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:94
msgid "Bake"
msgstr "烘焙"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:96
msgid "Rigid body simulations can be cached for stable playback and rendering."
msgstr "刚体模拟可以缓存，以实现稳定的播放和渲染。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:98
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Bake`: Bakes the rigid body simulation into Blender's "
"point cache for the current frame range."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Bake`：将当前帧范围内的刚体模拟烘焙到 Blender 的 *点缓存（Point Cache）* 中。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:99
msgid ""
":menuselection:`Delete Bake`: Clears the baked cache and restores real-"
"time simulation."
msgstr ":menuselection:`Delete Bake`：清除烘焙缓存，并恢复为实时模拟。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:101
msgid "When a bake exists:"
msgstr "当存在烘焙时："

#: ../../source/scene.rst:103
msgid "Timeline playback no longer recalculates physics"
msgstr "播放时间轴时不再重新计算物理"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:104
msgid "Simulation results are deterministic"
msgstr "模拟结果是确定的"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:105
msgid "Performance during animation playback improves"
msgstr "动画播放时性能提升"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:108
msgid "If you need to adjust rigid bodies or constraints, delete the bake first."
msgstr "如果你需要调整刚体或约束，请先删除烘焙。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:111
msgid "Workflow Notes"
msgstr "工作流程注意事项"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:113
msgid ""
"After duplicating, linking, or reorganizing the scene structure, it is "
"recommended to run :menuselection:`Update Rigid World`."
msgstr "在复制、链接或重新组织场景结构后，建议运行 :menuselection:`Update Rigid World`。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:114
msgid "Bake only after confirming that the simulation results behave as expected."
msgstr "确认模拟结果符合预期后再进行烘焙。"

#: ../../source/scene.rst:115
msgid ""
"When working in a multi-file workflow, run :menuselection:`Update Rigid "
"World` after using :menuselection:`Link` or :menuselection:`Library "
"Override` to avoid broken references."
msgstr ""
"在多文件工作流中，使用 :menuselection:`链接` 或 :menuselection:`库覆盖` "
"后，请运行 :menuselection:`Update Rigid World` 以避免引用断链。"

